works.description:
My photos are included in the website which was
taken  
during my vacation in Cebu and Boracay. These photos are not for public  
consumption. Apparently my pictures, together with the photos of the other
 
girls, came from the multiply site of the photographer, which is also a  
friend of mine. Apparently these photos were taken from the multiply site 

last 2007 and i just found these illegally posted pics now. I have a copy 

of the album in my multiply site where the photos are located. And as you 

can see in my multiply albums these photos are taken during my leisurely  
vacation in Boracay and Cebu.

So I am appealing that my photos be taken from the website. Given the  
nature of the website, it's defamatory on my part, and it's not proper for
 
my picture to be in that website.

Thank you and hoping for your immediate action as this site has been up  
since 2007.
